# Organization: Inclusive Growth Chain - https://inclusivegrowthchain.com/

As a Research Assistant at Inclusive Growth Chain, I contributed to the project focused on 
inclusive economic development and public policy. Working with the agri finance team, I supported research 
activities by conducting literature reviews, synthesizing evidence, analyzing qualitative and quantitative 
information, and preparing research outputs for partner organizations. The experience strengthened 
my ability to translate research into practical policy insights and recommendations while working across diverse 
development sectors. I was involved in practical implementation of the blockchain app in rural Tamil Nadu.

